300
00:18:37,726 --> 00:18:39,489
When did you see him?

301
00:18:39,728 --> 00:18:41,423
What else are you hiding from me?

302
00:18:43,599 --> 00:18:45,191
You don't trust me?

303
00:18:46,068 --> 00:18:47,831
You have no faith in me?

304
00:18:50,139 --> 00:18:52,164
I have no faith in myself

305
00:18:53,742 --> 00:18:55,903
I afraid I won't be good enough

306
00:18:57,212 --> 00:18:59,077
Afraid I cannot give you happiness

307
00:19:00,316 --> 00:19:02,079
Afraid of many other things

308
00:19:02,451 --> 00:19:04,316
Like what?

309
00:19:04,453 --> 00:19:06,478
