310
00:19:07,256 --> 00:19:09,383
I asked you to say "I like you"

311
00:19:10,259 --> 00:19:12,352
You said "I shouldn't"

312
00:19:14,096 --> 00:19:15,620
Do you know

313
00:19:15,898 --> 00:19:16,660
How a woman feels

314
00:19:16,732 --> 00:19:18,290
hearing that?

315
00:19:23,639 --> 00:19:25,937
Sounds like I have a crush on you

316
00:19:27,910 --> 00:19:29,377
I know

317
00:19:30,012 --> 00:19:32,378
You don't want the responsibility

318
00:19:34,016 --> 00:19:35,574
You're selfish

319
00:19:37,586 --> 00:19:40,214
Otherwise, say it

320
00:19:42,691 --> 00:19:45,489
I...

321
00:19:45,561 --> 00:19:46,858
I what?

322
00:19:48,063 --> 00:19:49,428
You can't say it

323
00:19:50,599 --> 00:19:52,658
Because you're the one just playing

324
00:19:55,904 --> 00:19:57,838
And you betrayed me

325
00:20:00,309 --> 00:20:01,799
Thank you

326
00:20:02,077 --> 00:20:04,671
Split the $3 million among yourselves

327
00:20:04,813 --> 00:20:07,509
No need, it's so much money

328
00:20:07,583 --> 00:20:11,349
No need...

329
00:20:13,889 --> 00:20:16,221
Henry, give it back!

330
00:20:16,492 --> 00:20:18,119
Thank you...

331
00:20:18,293 --> 00:20:19,817
Yuri, I didn't!

332
00:20:20,863 --> 00:20:22,956
No, you didn't like me

333
00:20:25,501 --> 00:20:27,799
I was wrong about you

334
00:20:33,642 --> 00:20:35,200
It's okay

335
00:20:38,313 --> 00:20:39,610
He bullied me

336
00:20:41,650 --> 00:20:43,641
Silly girl, no one does that when I'm around

337
00:20:43,919 --> 00:20:45,784
No one can harm you

338
00:20:48,390 --> 00:20:50,654
Too soft, I can't hear him

339
00:20:50,793 --> 00:20:52,021
I can't translate

340
00:20:52,528 --> 00:20:54,792
Mom, I'll return to Japan,

341
00:20:55,230 --> 00:20:56,219
Marry Kikukawa

342
00:20:58,100 --> 00:21:00,568
You scared me to death

343
00:21:00,636 --> 00:21:02,331
Let's go This way

344
00:21:02,438 --> 00:21:03,564
She said Let's go

345
00:21:03,639 --> 00:21:05,903
End of translation

346
00:22:01,997 --> 00:22:03,555
Great dancing!

347
00:22:03,732 --> 00:22:06,360
Everything's back to normal

348
00:22:11,540 --> 00:22:14,168
You worked hard, dry off

349
00:22:16,512 --> 00:22:17,706
Traitor!

350
00:22:17,946 --> 00:22:19,504
I didn't betray you

351
00:22:19,915 --> 00:22:21,212
They followed me.

352
00:22:21,483 --> 00:22:23,348
Could I stop them?

353
00:22:23,785 --> 00:22:25,878
They gave me money

354
00:22:28,824 --> 00:22:30,451
Could I refuse?

355
00:23:08,297 --> 00:23:10,595
Must we do that, too?

356
00:23:10,766 --> 00:23:11,960
Are you all right?

357
00:23:17,573 --> 00:23:18,665
Still angry?

358
00:23:18,907 --> 00:23:20,704
Will you feel better if you hit me?

359
00:23:21,109 --> 00:23:23,805
I'll let you!

360
00:23:24,379 --> 00:23:25,437
Hit me!

361
00:23:27,082 --> 00:23:30,950
I'll have 3 years bad luck

362
00:23:31,920 --> 00:23:33,512
Just once

363
00:23:45,734 --> 00:23:47,497
We've been friends...

364
00:23:47,769 --> 00:23:49,532
...since I left Malaysia

365
00:23:49,938 --> 00:23:53,396
Twenty years

366
00:23:54,042 --> 00:23:57,910
It's for your own good

367
00:23:58,847 --> 00:24:01,907
Your relationship had to be tested

368
00:24:02,117 --> 00:24:04,176
It's better to test it sooner

369
00:24:04,386 --> 00:24:05,819
So you can find out

370
00:24:07,189 --> 00:24:09,589
Are you still angry at me?

371
00:24:10,125 --> 00:24:11,956
Are you?

372
00:24:16,965 --> 00:24:18,330
Stop

373
00:24:21,103 --> 00:24:23,367
Can't you see I've changed?

374
00:24:24,106 --> 00:24:25,437
Let's have fun!

375
00:24:26,074 --> 00:24:27,541
That's right

376
00:24:28,210 --> 00:24:30,178
Leave some for me

377
00:24:31,580 --> 00:24:34,048
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

378
00:24:36,151 --> 00:24:37,618
Hi!

379
00:24:38,954 --> 00:24:40,012
You're here

380
00:24:40,756 --> 00:24:44,852
We came to see you

381
00:24:47,429 --> 00:24:49,556
You're not so cool today

382
00:24:49,731 --> 00:24:51,631
He's hot now

383
00:24:53,101 --> 00:24:55,160
When can we go out?

384
00:24:55,370 --> 00:24:56,928
You won't turn off your phone?

385
00:24:57,439 --> 00:24:59,873
Call me, I'll keep it on...

386
00:25:00,275 --> 00:25:01,264
...for you

387
00:25:01,643 --> 00:25:03,304
You turned it off for me

388
00:25:04,246 --> 00:25:06,942
You're different

389
00:25:08,316 --> 00:25:09,510
Come!

390
00:25:11,353 --> 00:25:15,847
Can you handle both?

391
00:25:16,391 --> 00:25:18,086
Let me have one

392
00:25:18,360 --> 00:25:20,954
What?

393
00:25:21,997 --> 00:25:23,521
What?

394
00:25:25,133 --> 00:25:28,159
Selfishness brings bad luck

395
00:25:29,237 --> 00:25:31,137
- Stop it!
- Where to?

396
00:25:31,473 --> 00:25:32,770
Your home

397
00:25:33,141 --> 00:25:34,438
What for?

398
00:25:34,643 --> 00:25:36,634
Coffee

399
00:25:36,712 --> 00:25:38,145
Let's go, don't want to see

400
00:25:40,949 --> 00:25:41,677
Am I famous?

401
00:25:41,750 --> 00:25:45,618
For my coffee?

402
00:25:45,954 --> 00:25:47,012
Got it!

403
00:25:47,856 --> 00:25:50,654
Coffee time

404
00:25:51,093 --> 00:25:53,061
Where's the coffee?

405
00:25:58,233 --> 00:25:59,666
Where are you?

406
00:26:05,574 --> 00:26:08,099
What are you looking at?

407
00:26:08,176 --> 00:26:09,700
Aren't you getting coffee for us?

408
00:26:09,911 --> 00:26:11,344
Who are they?

409
00:26:12,781 --> 00:26:14,874
- Where are you?
- Wait!

410
00:26:16,718 --> 00:26:18,481
March 31

411
00:26:26,595 --> 00:26:29,587
Marriage? Whose?

412
00:26:40,108 --> 00:26:41,803
Dreamy Wong!

413
00:26:44,279 --> 00:26:45,837
Coco?

414
00:26:48,150 --> 00:26:50,118
Why are you here?

415
00:26:52,120 --> 00:26:54,020
You want fulfillment?

416
00:26:59,027 --> 00:27:01,461
Might as well be me

417
00:27:02,631 --> 00:27:04,064
I'm not so bad

418
00:27:05,233 --> 00:27:06,461
Don't do that

419
00:27:07,602 --> 00:27:11,038
You want a twosome?

420
00:27:11,540 --> 00:27:12,768
Nancy!

421
00:27:15,477 --> 00:27:18,969
Okay, you're a bore

422
00:27:19,181 --> 00:27:22,150
But for a friend

423
00:27:22,918 --> 00:27:25,443
What are you doing? Get up!

424
00:27:26,021 --> 00:27:27,648
Here's one more!

425
00:27:27,923 --> 00:27:29,185
Although I'm not gay

426
00:27:29,758 --> 00:27:32,090
You wouldn't share with me just now

427
00:27:32,227 --> 00:27:33,819
I'll let you do it!

428
00:27:34,296 --> 00:27:35,991
For my good friend...

429
00:27:36,064 --> 00:27:37,691
...who was hurt by love

430
00:27:38,133 --> 00:27:41,864
I sacrifice myself

431
00:27:45,674 --> 00:27:48,939
To rescue you from the abyss

432
00:27:49,110 --> 00:27:50,577
Although I'm too plump

433
00:27:52,247 --> 00:27:55,478
Hope you don't mind

434
00:27:55,684 --> 00:27:57,584
You got it wrong

435
00:27:58,320 --> 00:27:59,617
Am I like that?

436
00:28:00,188 --> 00:28:01,815
It's only a coffee date

437
00:28:02,023 --> 00:28:03,513
I know you're not like that

438
00:28:03,725 --> 00:28:04,817
You miss Yuri

439
00:28:05,126 --> 00:28:06,423
I'm not through yet

440
00:28:06,494 --> 00:28:07,722
Don't try to stop me

441
00:28:07,829 --> 00:28:08,955
Philip!

442
00:28:10,866 --> 00:28:12,128
I've decided

443
00:28:18,840 --> 00:28:20,637
I'm going to Japan tomorrow for her

444
00:28:22,010 --> 00:28:23,807
I don't care

445
00:28:25,947 --> 00:28:27,312
As a traitor...

446
00:28:28,316 --> 00:28:31,410
I should repay you by going with you

447
00:28:31,820 --> 00:28:33,082
We'll go, too

448
00:28:33,288 --> 00:28:34,619
Are you traitors?

449
00:28:34,823 --> 00:28:36,256
With passports?

450
00:28:36,825 --> 00:28:39,020
You know the way, Traitor?

451
00:28:39,694 --> 00:28:40,888
It's easy

452
00:28:41,263 --> 00:28:44,096
Fly to Narita Airport, Tokyo

453
00:28:44,633 --> 00:28:45,759
I know that

454
00:28:45,901 --> 00:28:47,493
Take the JR Express...

455
00:28:47,602 --> 00:28:48,933
...to Shinjuku Exit

456
00:28:49,004 --> 00:28:50,096
When you get out of the station,

457
00:28:50,171 --> 00:28:52,264
There's a Sakura Department Store there

458
00:28:53,308 --> 00:28:56,175
See?

459
00:28:56,344 --> 00:28:57,777
Here's one

460
00:28:58,313 --> 00:29:00,372
How can we find her?

461
00:29:01,483 --> 00:29:02,916
Start with this branch

462
00:29:03,485 --> 00:29:04,543
That's crazy

463
00:29:05,053 --> 00:29:06,714
Sakura Enterprises

464
00:29:07,022 --> 00:29:09,115
Wedding-tomorrow-11:00 a.m.

465
00:29:09,190 --> 00:29:12,125
- Summer Shrine

466
00:29:13,328 --> 00:29:15,489
Let's crash the party!

467
00:29:31,413 --> 00:29:34,905
The wedding has just started

468
00:30:11,853 --> 00:30:12,820
Hurry!

469
00:30:12,887 --> 00:30:15,754
After she drinks

470
00:30:15,824 --> 00:30:17,883
They'll be legally married!

471
00:30:18,093 --> 00:30:19,117
Say it now

472
00:30:20,428 --> 00:30:21,292
I object!

473
00:30:22,063 --> 00:30:23,087
Yuri!

474
00:30:23,398 --> 00:30:25,059
I object!

475
00:30:25,467 --> 00:30:26,365
I object!

476
00:30:26,634 --> 00:30:27,760
I object!

477
00:30:30,505 --> 00:30:32,370
- Get them out!
- Yuri!

478
00:30:34,142 --> 00:30:35,905
I must speak to you!

479
00:30:35,977 --> 00:30:37,569
- Say it!
- Yuri!

480
00:30:37,645 --> 00:30:39,306
Mom, the press is here

481
00:30:40,015 --> 00:30:42,643
Don't use violence

482
00:30:43,018 --> 00:30:44,542
Yuri!

483
00:30:46,287 --> 00:30:47,413
Let him speak

484
00:30:51,893 --> 00:30:53,451
Let go of him

485
00:31:00,235 --> 00:31:01,532
Speak

486
00:31:05,473 --> 00:31:07,270
Many told me to come

487
00:31:08,276 --> 00:31:11,268
But most of all

488
00:31:11,846 --> 00:31:13,245
I wanted to

489
00:31:13,982 --> 00:31:15,506
Because most of all, I feared...

490
00:31:16,518 --> 00:31:17,985
...losing you

491
00:31:19,487 --> 00:31:21,182
If I didn't come

492
00:31:22,257 --> 00:31:23,554
I'd regret it...

493
00:31:23,892 --> 00:31:25,621
...all my life

494
00:31:27,996 --> 00:31:29,554
I was always...

495
00:31:31,099 --> 00:31:32,589
...insecure

496
00:31:33,368 --> 00:31:35,302
and lack of self confidence

497
00:31:37,172 --> 00:31:40,938
Saw only black and white

498
00:31:42,977 --> 00:31:44,604
Then I met you

499
00:31:45,814 --> 00:31:48,214
I felt colours

500
00:31:49,617 --> 00:31:51,050
You...

501
00:31:51,719 --> 00:31:54,654
...filled my life with colour

502
00:31:56,024 --> 00:31:58,584
You appreciate me the most

503
00:31:59,928 --> 00:32:01,361
You said...

504
00:32:02,297 --> 00:32:03,889
...you chose cherry blossoms

505
00:32:04,999 --> 00:32:06,489
For their...

506
00:32:07,102 --> 00:32:08,729
...short-lived glory

507
00:32:10,071 --> 00:32:11,868
I tell you

508
00:32:13,575 --> 00:32:16,169
I choose that, too

509
00:32:17,278 --> 00:32:19,508
So I had to take this chance

510
00:32:21,149 --> 00:32:22,810
I may not be able...

511
00:32:23,518 --> 00:32:27,215
...to change your mind

512
00:32:27,489 --> 00:32:29,116
But I must say it

513
00:32:30,558 --> 00:32:32,822
I dared not say these words

514
00:32:36,331 --> 00:32:39,562
I feared losing you

515
00:32:42,937 --> 00:32:44,234
But...

516
00:32:44,706 --> 00:32:47,106
...if I dare not say them

517
00:32:47,842 --> 00:32:50,538
I cannot tell you

518
00:32:51,446 --> 00:32:53,710
I'll take care of you all your life

519
00:32:56,184 --> 00:32:57,446
Yuri...

520
00:32:59,053 --> 00:33:00,543
I love you!

521
00:33:04,159 --> 00:33:05,626
I love you?

522
00:33:15,737 --> 00:33:17,170
I'm touched

523
00:33:17,572 --> 00:33:18,664
Thank you

524
00:33:20,775 --> 00:33:23,676
This is the best wedding gift

525
00:33:27,448 --> 00:33:29,109
But sorry

526
00:33:30,051 --> 00:33:31,882
You're too late

527
00:33:47,802 --> 00:33:50,202
I wish to complete the ceremony

528
00:33:54,909 --> 00:33:56,809
Go now

529
00:34:30,478 --> 00:34:32,844
Give him this, a present

530
00:34:32,914 --> 00:34:36,350
To thank him for coming

531
00:34:36,584 --> 00:34:38,245
Yes, sir

532
00:34:42,357 --> 00:34:45,224
Take this, from them

533
00:34:45,793 --> 00:34:47,920
Thanks for coming

534
00:34:49,063 --> 00:34:50,621
You may go

535
00:35:02,677 --> 00:35:06,113
Pardon us

536
00:35:06,814 --> 00:35:08,645
Sorry

537
00:36:23,491 --> 00:36:27,689
What a waste

538
00:36:32,500 --> 00:36:34,161
You didn't open the fan?

539
00:36:34,268 --> 00:36:36,099
Don't want to

540
00:36:38,039 --> 00:36:39,472
Don't take my fan!

541
00:36:39,607 --> 00:36:42,542
No, look

542
00:36:42,710 --> 00:36:45,577
April 1 st, that's today

543
00:36:45,713 --> 00:36:46,907
I'll wait for you...

544
00:36:46,981 --> 00:36:48,505
...at 11 a.m.

545
00:36:48,583 --> 00:36:49,777
Ueno Park

546
00:36:50,084 --> 00:36:52,746
One hour ago, not too bad

547
00:36:53,454 --> 00:36:55,718
She's already married

548
00:36:57,158 --> 00:36:58,682
And it's April Fool's Day

549
00:36:59,160 --> 00:37:00,457
Up to you

550
00:37:01,095 --> 00:37:04,064
It's okay to be late

551
00:37:04,599 --> 00:37:06,533
We're leaving

552
00:37:59,587 --> 00:38:01,145
Please, stop!

553
00:38:01,222 --> 00:38:02,621
Great! Hurry!

554
00:38:49,070 --> 00:38:50,059
Hi!

555
00:38:50,905 --> 00:38:52,566
Are you looking for someone?

556
00:38:52,740 --> 00:38:53,672
You are...

557
00:38:54,175 --> 00:38:55,301
You don't know me

558
00:38:55,409 --> 00:38:56,876
But you should know my lover

559
00:38:57,011 --> 00:38:59,275
His name is Shunichi Kikukawa

560
00:39:00,681 --> 00:39:02,649
Shinjuku... Colour?

561
00:39:03,417 --> 00:39:04,850
I don't understand

562
00:39:05,119 --> 00:39:06,677
Or Kikukawa Shunichi

563
00:39:07,021 --> 00:39:08,113
Kikukawa Shun...

564
00:39:10,391 --> 00:39:11,585
...ichi?

565
00:39:12,126 --> 00:39:13,593
Hello

566
00:39:14,595 --> 00:39:17,063
My girlfriend

567
00:39:19,200 --> 00:39:20,599
Excuse me?

568
00:39:26,173 --> 00:39:29,199
Yuri's and my late fathers were friends

569
00:39:30,344 --> 00:39:33,177
They planned our wedding

570
00:39:34,949 --> 00:39:37,816
In conjunction...

571
00:39:37,885 --> 00:39:40,649
...with our companies merging

572
00:39:45,092 --> 00:39:47,287
When the news spread

573
00:39:47,528 --> 00:39:50,827
Our share prices kept going up

574
00:39:57,638 --> 00:39:59,606
To maintain this trend

575
00:39:59,941 --> 00:40:02,034
Even though Yuri and I...

576
00:40:02,310 --> 00:40:04,608
...are like siblings

577
00:40:05,580 --> 00:40:08,048
We had to get married

578
00:40:08,249 --> 00:40:09,876
Which I needed,

579
00:40:10,017 --> 00:40:11,609
to get my inheritance

580
00:40:13,854 --> 00:40:17,790
But she nearly canceled for you

581
00:40:19,160 --> 00:40:21,651
Fortunately at the airport

582
00:40:21,829 --> 00:40:24,764
I was able to explain it to her

583
00:40:25,466 --> 00:40:27,331
And she was willing

584
00:40:27,468 --> 00:40:30,631
To be my wife in name

585
00:40:32,940 --> 00:40:36,876
She also wanted to test you

586
00:40:39,246 --> 00:40:41,305
We were worried

587
00:40:42,717 --> 00:40:44,446
But you came

588
00:40:44,619 --> 00:40:47,520
The fan was not made in vain

589
00:40:49,023 --> 00:40:51,287
We'll secretly...

590
00:40:51,492 --> 00:40:53,551
...divorce soon

591
00:40:55,596 --> 00:40:57,120
Where is she?

592
00:40:58,633 --> 00:41:00,225
Dreamy Wong!

593
00:41:00,668 --> 00:41:01,930
You're late!

594
00:41:08,709 --> 00:41:10,233
Come, see the cherry blossoms

595
00:41:10,311 --> 00:41:11,710
- Goodbye!
- Goodbye!

596
00:41:11,979 --> 00:41:13,344
Goodbye...

597
00:42:03,931 --> 00:42:04,727
I've been practicing

598
00:42:10,438 --> 00:42:11,530
Come
